div.p: This is a copy of an image on Commons, uploaded as a local copy to allow it to be protected. It is protected because it is used in several system messages.
The description from the Commons copy follows:
The Wikimedia Commons logo, SVG version.
This version created by Pumbaa80, using a proper partial circle and SVG geometry features. (Former versions used to be slightly warped.)
SVG version euh created by User:Grunt and cleaned up by User:3247, based on the earlier PNG version, created by User:Reidab.
Message from the original creator, Reidab:

dl.dd: "I'd be happy for the copyright to be transfered to the Wikimedia Foundation. I'll clean it up a bit and then sent it off to you. I think that illustrator can export to an svg, but if it can't, I'll send is as an eps."

div.p: Our logo policy is that the logo copyright is held by the Wikimedia Foundation.
